=== ERRORS FIXED ===

FILE: lib/features/chanting/presentation/pages/chant_counter_page.dart
  LINE 392: final dynamic onTap;
  ISSUE: onTap field typed as `dynamic`, dynamic call via `() => onTap()`
         loses type safety and triggers avoid_dynamic_calls lint.
  FIX:  Changed `final dynamic onTap` -> `final VoidCallback onTap`
        Changed `onTap: () => onTap()` -> `onTap: onTap`
        VoidCallback accepts both sync and async callbacks (Future<void> is
        assignable to void in Dart's type system).

